<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>SignalRoutes</title>
  </head>

  <body style="font-family: system-ui, sans-serif; margin: 0; background: #f8f7f4; color: #1a1a1a;">
    
    <main style="max-width: 860px; margin: 60px auto; padding: 20px;">
      
      <!-- HEADER -->
      <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:16px; margin-bottom:30px;">
        <img src="/logo.png" alt="SignalRoutes logo" style="width:60px;" />
        <h1 style="margin:0; font-size:32px;">SignalRoutes</h1>
      </div>

      <p style="font-weight:600; font-size:18px; margin-bottom:10px;">
        Clear signals. Better decisions.
      </p>

      <p style="margin-bottom:40px; line-height:1.6;">
        SignalRoutes builds a suite of apps designed to help people make better decisions. 
        From personal finance (SpendScore) and news clarity (SourceBrief), to founder guidance (FounderRoutes) 
        and regulatory compliance (ComplianceIQ), every product is built to cut through noise and deliver clarity.
      </p>

      <!-- PRODUCTS -->
      <h2 style="margin-bottom:20px;">Products</h2>

      <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:18px;">

        <!-- FounderRoutes -->
        <div style="display:flex; gap:16px; padding:16px; border-radius:12px; background:white; border:1px solid #e5e5e5;">
          <img src="/founderroutes.png" style="width:42px; height:42px;" />
          <div>
            <strong>FounderRoutes</strong><br />
            Build your business with clarity. Know what to do now—and what not to do.<br />
            <a href="https://founder-routes-app-rep-production.up.railway.app/">Visit →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- SpendScore -->
        <div style="display:flex; gap:16px; padding:16px; border-radius:12px; background:white; border:1px solid #e5e5e5;">
          <img src="/spendscore.png" style="width:42px; height:42px;" />
          <div>
            <strong>SpendScore</strong><br />
            Understand your money in real time. Build better habits without complexity.<br />
            <em>Launching April 1 on Google Play</em>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- SourceBrief -->
        <div style="display:flex; gap:16px; padding:16px; border-radius:12px; background:white; border:1px solid #e5e5e5;">
          <img src="/sourcebrief.png" style="width:42px; height:42px;" />
          <div>
            <strong>SourceBrief</strong><br />
            The news, distilled. What matters. What’s true. Nothing extra.<br />
            <a href="https://forms.gle/2y9sG2d2zt2dABFj9" target="_blank"
   style="display:inline-block; margin-top:10px; padding:10px 16px; background:#1a1a1a; color:white; border-radius:6px; text-decoration:none;">
  Join Waitlist
</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- ComplianceIQ -->
        <div style="display:flex; gap:16px; padding:16px; border-radius:12px; background:white; border:1px solid #e5e5e5;">
          <div style="width:42px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;">⚖️</div>
          <div>
            <strong>ComplianceIQ</strong><br />
            Stay ahead of compliance without drowning in updates.<br />
            <em>Coming soon</em>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- WHAT WE DO -->
      <h2 style="margin-top:50px;">What We Do</h2>

      <p style="line-height:1.6;">
        Every product we build solves the same problem at a different level:
      </p>

      <ul style="line-height:1.8;">
        <li><strong>Information</strong> → SourceBrief</li>
        <li><strong>Money</strong> → SpendScore</li>
        <li><strong>Business</strong> → FounderRoutes</li>
        <li><strong>Regulation</strong> → ComplianceIQ</li>
      </ul>

      <p style="font-weight:600; margin-top:20px;">
        Clarity first. Direction next.
      </p>

    </main>

  </body>
</html>
